      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">PGI 237.102-76</ph> Review criteria
for the acquisition of services.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">The tenets of the DoD-wide architecture for the acquisition
of services along with the associated review criteria are available <xref href="http://www.acq.osd.mil/dpap/dars/pgi/docs/Criteria_for_Acquisition_of_Services_(Pre_and_Postaward).doc"
                  class="- topic/xref "
                  scope="external"
                  format="doc"/>.
These matrices are to be used when conducting reviews in the preaward
phase (Review/Approval of Acquisition Strategies or Preaward Peer
Reviews) and in the postaward phase (Postaward Peer Reviews). See
DFARS <xref href="201.170.dita#DFARS-201.170"
                  base="DFARS-201.170"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">201.170</xref>, Peer reviews,
and PGI <ph xtrc="PGIxref" class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref href="PGI_201.170.dita#DFARS-PGI_PGI_201.170"
                     base="DFARS-PGI_PGI_201.170"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">201.170</xref>
            </ph>,
Peer reviews.</p>
